in use.


> 20011001 is ?
> 
> 10 oct 2001 ?
> 01 jan 2001 ?
> 


1 Oct 2001, whereas "01/10/2001" would be read as Jan 10, 2001 or Oct 1,
2001 in differents part of the world.

Using language-specific codes are fine and well only if you know for sure
which language was used.

